parameters:
Voice Priestess Phoni: Everyone, thank you for coming! Since
you're here, would you like to have a meal together?

Village Chief Olden: I have heard the story from my
daughter. We confronted the dragon that we had escaped from
once again.

Village Chief Olden: The word 'hero' may sound cliché, but
to all of you heroes, thank you for protecting our homeland.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Clea and the others are truly
amazing. They have not only changed us, but even the empire!

\CL 【Voice Priestess Phoni's After Story】As the new
priestess, she tackled various problems throughout the
empire. She also cooperated with the Adventurer's Guild and
the Magic Academy.

\Cl The special feelings towards Clea never disappeared
throughout my life, but I met my destined partner and got
married. We were blessed with a beautiful girl.

\Cl By the way, it seems that Phoni's destined partner was a
handsome young man who resembled Clea...

\CL 【Village Chief Olden's After Story】There were criticisms
from some of the villagers regarding the new way of the
priestess, but Olden took the lead and spent time persuading
them.

\CL Gradually, the relationship between Phoni and her child
was repaired, and the old man transformed into an overly
doting grandfather when Phoni gave birth to a child.

\CL It was something that even Clea and the others were
amazed by.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

You won't be able to come back, but are you really leaving
the room?
Clea (We haven't talked yet, have we?)

3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea: Thank you for helping me. I'm really happy to have met
a friend like Phoni.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Me too, Clea. Because you were here,
I was able to take a new step forward.

Voice Priestess Phoni: The days we adventured together...
they shine like precious jewels and will never fade away, I
believe.

Mage Relm: Voice magic is truly fascinating... No, no, it's
not right to step into something precious with dirty shoes,
is it?

Voice Priestess Phoni: If there is a possibility of the
priestess lineage coming to an end, I will secretly consult
with you. The power of voice magic has the ability to save
many people, so I have that strength.

Mage Relm: I pray that it doesn't come to that. While my
interest in magic is endless, I also value the traditions of
the priestess.
Thief Nora: The dish you made for me was delicious!

Voice Priestess Phoni: Hehe, if you'd like, please come and
eat. There are still many local specialties in the village
of Iremo.

Thief Nora: Is it okay?! I'll come and play with Clea-san
and the others!

Priestess Sophia: The journey as a new priestess... I truly
think it's wonderful.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Thank you very much. The path I have
chosen may be similar to that of a priestess.

Priestess Sophia: I will strive to become a priestess that
you can be proud of...

Village Chief Olden: Thank you for helping Phoni grow. I am
grateful that you have allowed me to grow as a father
figure.
